### git tag

"git tag" is used to mark specific commits, usually for releases.

---

Create a Lightweight Tag

git tag v1.0

Create an Annotated Tag (Recommended)

git tag -a v1.0 -m "Release version 1.0"

List Tags

git tag

Push Tags to Remote

git push origin v1.0

